data.description: Rare and sprawling 1-acre ranch home located in the desirable Highland Estates. From the grandeur of vaulted ceilings to the warmth of a hearth room and the grace of a formal dining area, this home provides a haven of comfort and is perfect for gatherings of friends & family. The primary bedroom with a spacious ensuite, complemented by a split bedroom floor plan ensures a private retreat. Enjoy the leisure of the vast, leveled backyard that also boasts a covered patio. Main floor laundry, convenient to shopping and major highways, this residence nestled in the heart of Wentzville has so much to offer.
